{
  "name": "@wuyonghui0810/vkey-bid-standardizer",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "银行投标响应文档标准化工具（v1.0）。7 条流水线：all/fix/renumber/auto-number/review/convert-md/validate-patterns",
